# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Wallpapers (add your own, don't commit large binaries)
# wallpapers/Pictures/Wallpapers/*.jpg
# wallpapers/Pictures/Wallpapers/*.jpeg
# wallpapers/Pictures/Wallpapers/*.png
# wallpapers/Pictures/Wallpapers/*.webp
# !wallpapers/Pictures/Wallpapers/.gitkeep

# Theme engine runtime output (PIPE-03/D-05) — generated colors live in
# ~/.local/state/theme/, outside this repo. Two consumers have no native
# @import/include mechanism (walker, yazi, D-07) so theme-engine wires their
# config path directly with a symlink into the state dir; since both live
# under whole-package stow symlinks back into this repo tree, the symlink
# theme-apply creates lands at these exact repo-relative paths — ignore it.
walker/.config/walker/themes/rice/style.css
yazi/.config/yazi/theme.toml

# Screenshots (D-48) — runtime output from screenshot.sh, never repo content.
# Belt-and-suspenders alongside the .stow-local-ignore fold exclusion above.
wallpapers/Pictures/Screenshots/
